videos.headline: WVU's Grier fires an 82-yard TD to open scoring
videos.description: Marcus Simms hauls in a deep toss from Will Grier for an 82-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: West Virginia comes up with a 4th-down-stop
videos.description: WVU's defense pummels Kansas State's Alex Barnes in the backfield to force a turnover on downs.

videos.headline: Grier throws 2nd TD pass vs. Kansas State
videos.description: David Sills V hauls in a 1-yard slant pass from Will Grier for a West Virginia touchdown

videos.headline: Will Grier launches 62-yard TD pass
videos.description: Tevin Bush runs away from his defender after grabbing Will Grier's fourth passing touchdown.

videos.headline: Grier throws 5th TD pass vs. Kansas St
videos.description: Will Grier connects with Davids Sills V on a touchdown strike for the third time, increasing WVU's lead over Kansas State.
